♪

19:34.383 --> 19:36.367
Who are you here for?

19:36.402 --> 19:38.536
Don't you get it?
He's here for you.

19:38.570 --> 19:40.371
It's always been you.

19:40.406 --> 19:42.240
You guys are best friends.

19:42.274 --> 19:46.978
And it was wrong of me to try and take
something that special away from you.

19:47.012 --> 19:50.248
Right? Unless, maybe,
you changed your mind?

19:50.282 --> 19:51.399
♪

19:51.450 --> 19:52.950
(quietly):
No.

19:52.985 --> 19:55.520
I'm here for Steve.

